            img.tj-emoji(draggable='false', alt='ðŸŒ¬', src='https://twemoji.maxcdn.com/2/72x72/1f32c.png')
            span=' Shoo, shoo!'
          p
            span Anyways, you may want to try going back to the
            span=' '
            a.lk-link(href='/writers', aria-label='Back to Pony Foo contributing author list') list of writers
